# Title: File Download Via Bitsadmin
# Author: Michael Haag, FPT.EagleEye
# Date: 2017-03-09
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of bitsadmin downloading a file
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.persistence, attack.t1197, attack.s0190, attack.t1036.003
# False Positives:
#   - Some legitimate apps use this, but limited.

Image="*\\bitsadmin.exe" OR OriginalFileName="bitsadmin.exe" CommandLine="* /transfer *" OR (CommandLine IN ("* /create *", "* /addfile *") CommandLine="*http*") | table CommandLine,ParentCommandLine